author: Courier Staff
title: Winfield to host volleyball sub-state
text: High school volleyball sub-state locations were released Wednesday by the Kansas High School Athletic Association. All teams will play Oct. 24. Winfield will host Coffeyville-Field Kindley, Independence and Wellington in the 4A Division I playoff. Douglass will travel to Conway Springs along with Belle Plaine, Cheney, Conway Springs, Garden Plain, Bluestem, Whitewater Remington and Wichita Independent. Oxford and Udall volleyball teams will travel to Greensburg.
